    <item>
      <title>Blushing Betty</title>
      <link>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/blushing-betty/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2018 11:17:51 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/blushing-betty/</guid>
      <description>
&lt;ul class=&#34;ingredients&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;1½ oz bourbon&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;1 oz grapefruit juice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;½ oz simple syrup&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;grapefruit twist&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;



&lt;div class=&#34;instructions e-instructions&#34;&gt;
  Shake vigorously with ice. Strain into rocks glass over fresh ice.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Garnish with grapefruit twist.
&lt;/div&gt;


</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Maple Leaf</title>
      <link>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/maple-leaf/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2018 11:17:51 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/maple-leaf/</guid>
      <description>
&lt;div class=&#34;recipe-intro p-summary&#34;&gt;The recipe where I found this drink said, “drink on a porch with an old dog.” It’s solid advice.&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;ul class=&#34;ingredients&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;2 oz bourbon&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;¾ oz real maple syrup&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;¾ oz lemon juice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;cinnamon stick&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;



&lt;div class=&#34;instructions e-instructions&#34;&gt;
  Shake vigorously with ice. Strain into rocks glass over crushed ice.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Garnish with cinnamon stick.
&lt;/div&gt;


</description>
